Insurance Release Notes

2024 Insurance Release Notes
Elevate the Self-Service Experience of Insurance Policyholders
Improve Customer Interactions with Quick Summaries Using Einstein Copilot for Insurance (Beta)
OmniStudio DataRaptor Has a New Name in Insurance
Track Marketing Email Events on Engagement Timeline for Enhanced Customer Interactions

Discover how you can provide your customers with quick access to policy and claim details with the Financial Services Client Portal for FSC Insurance. Use Einstein Copilot for Insurance to help your customer service representatives save time and effort by generating quick record summaries.

Insurance Policyholder Portal
Ensure better control, convenience, and efficiency for clients through self-service capabilities such as consolidated views of policies and claims.

Einstein Copilot for Insurance
Save time and effort by streamlining business tasks with conversational AI. Gain quick customer insights using AI-generated summaries of Account, Insurance Policy, and Claim records.

Omnistudio Data Mapper (Formerly DataRaptor)
Renamed to improve consistency in feature names and labels.

Engagement Timeline
Get a chronological view of customer engagements with marketing email communication for a specific Account in Salesforce.

Note: This release is in preview. Features described here don't become generally available until the latest general availability date that Salesforce announces for this release.
title: Elevate Insurance Policyholder Experience
